<h1>Options</h1>
<p>Here at Health is Wealth we have plenty of different activites that you may partake in which is what makes us such a diverse fitness center.</p>
<h2>Basketball Courts</h2>
<p>Our fitness center comes equipped with a full court Basketball arena with 2 main 10 ft rims with smaller rims on the side for children.</p>
<h3>Sauna</h3>
<p>After a long workout come step in to our fully equipped Sauna it will enchance your recovery process by increasing your 
blood circulation and will relax your muscles.</p>
<h4>Swimming pool and Jacuzzi</h4>
<p>After a workout sometime you just need to cool down, well you can do that in our swimming pools which is also really good for your cardiovascular health. 
Our jacuzzi is will also soothe your sore tired muscles.</p>
<h4>Food/Smoothie bar</h4>
<p>You might also be interested in a nice meal or smoothie after your workout, 
all of our meals and smoothies are healthy and will help get you your daily protein dose which is a must for trying to build muscle and it's also very refreshing.</p>

